


                                   AM C SOURCES

                                       VOL1


Why AM C Sources?

Because if you are reading this docs you like C programming language
Because every programmer is always looking for source code :-)
Because froma a little source code you could raise a big project
Because in my free time i enjoy myself porting little pieces of software.
Because you are in need of this unfindable example code.
Because is good to have all sources just under your hands.

What is  AM C Sources?


AM  C  Sources  is  a  simple  collection  of  usefull  C  and C++ programs and 
algorithms easily browsable.

What AM C Sources is not.

AM C Sources is not a programming course.
The author is non responsable for any malfunction of source codes.

Bug Reports

Bug reports are welcome, but the author doesn't guarantee the correction.
In  the  next volumes,  will  be added a  bug list  and maybe the correction of
these bugs.

