HELP ME! :-)

Let  me  know  if  you find this collection interesting, if i won't receive any 
message i will stop the developement of this project.

Help me in making this collection grow up.

Surely if u are a programmer  you  have some project stored on your  hd by long 
ime. Why  dont  you  release  them  as  freeware so that other people can  take 
inspiration from them?

Don't be afraid to send me sources!

Requrements:

- All sources must be in C or C++.
- You have to make a small readme file.


